# === Archives ===
*.zip
*.tar
*.tar.gz
*.tgz

# === Negations: explicitly keep these committed ===
# Project-level Claude guide.
!CLAUDE.md
# Parity fixtures generated from reference NumPy SWAMPE.
!unit_tests/fixtures/*.npz
# Baseline summary from the long-run parity script (used for drift tracking).
!testing/long_run_parity_outputs/
!testing/long_run_parity_outputs/*/
!testing/long_run_parity_outputs/*/summary.json
